title: Darin - Exit 2013 (Ltd) - 2CD 2013
description:
Exit is the sixth studio album by Swedish singer/songwriter Darin Zanyar. The album was released on January 30, 2013 and debut at number one on Swedish Charts. Exit was certified Gold on its first week of release. The album includes the platinum-selling hit Nobody Knows.
